@group configuration
@endpoint GET /configuration/account/encryption
@desc Retrieves information about the default encryption configuration for the Amazon Web Services account in the default or specified Region. For more information, see Key management in the IoT SiteWise User Guide.
@returns(200) {encryptionType: str, kmsKeyArn: str?, configurationStatus: ConfigurationStatus{state: str, error: ConfigurationErrorDetails?{code: str, message: str}}}

